Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.32,0:01:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾瑞尔，晚饭好像快好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.33,0:01:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.23,0:01:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你决定了什么事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.03,0:01:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看得出来吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.64,0:01:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我陪伴你很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.44,0:01:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看样子该结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.32,0:02:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱的魔力已经变得相当的强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.49,0:02:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样她一定可以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.66,0:02:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们再不来吃，炖肉会冷掉的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.83,0:02:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，我马上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.43,0:02:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我辛辛苦苦煮给你们吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.70,0:02:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果艾瑞尔与斯比都…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.91,0:02:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们看，你们看，你们看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.13,0:02:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第68话 小樱与过去的库洛里德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.22,0:03:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶，这些雪是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.16,0:03:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是没用吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.40,0:03:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能光顾着逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.17,0:03:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要想办法对付雪人们…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.49,0:04:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然你们这样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.23,0:04:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,库洛创造的库洛牌啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.27,0:04:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舍弃旧有姿态\N重新转生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.04,0:04:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以新主人，小樱之名命令你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.51,0:04:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“雪”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.28,0:04:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪啊，把他们都埋起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.50,0:05:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次小樱又解决了问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.92,0:05:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只差一点点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.82,0:05:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请加油，小樱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.96,0:05:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.93,0:05:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知世，小狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.29,0:05:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.00,0:05:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太遗憾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.70,0:05:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做了一套新的战斗服\N本来想让你穿上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.54,0:05:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次发生什么怪事时\N你一定一定要穿上喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.04,0:05:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果怪事接二连三的发生\N我也会很困扰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.38,0:05:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.85,0:05:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有你在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.75,0:06:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，是啊\N你克服了许多难题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.29,0:06:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把库洛牌都变成小樱牌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.76,0:06:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好小樱可以变成\N比库洛还了不起的魔法师喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.16,0:06:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.36,0:06:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼你也这么想吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.14,0:06:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，还早得很
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.84,0:06:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要追上库洛，还差一大截
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.14,0:06:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说话干嘛那么认真啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.54,0:06:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是说实话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.39,0:06:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,库洛先生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.64,0:06:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了，你睡不着吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.11,0:07:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小可\N库洛先生是什么样的人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.85,0:07:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么突然这么问？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.55,0:07:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得很在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.69,0:07:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才你们也说过吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.09,0:07:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以我现在的魔力\N不管什么事都能应付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.46,0:07:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过，月说我还差一大截
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.06,0:07:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.90,0:07:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月会那么在意库洛\N是有其他的原因啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.17,0:07:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不会想起库洛先生吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.07,0:07:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，他的确很令人难忘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.55,0:07:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.65,0:07:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过那是很久以前的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.65,0:07:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我的主人是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.35,0:07:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过我还不像库洛先生\N那样魔力高强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.49,0:07:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生怪事时\N也只能拼命的设法解决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.56,0:07:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想如果是库洛先生\N一定不会发生这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.63,0:07:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我当你们的新主人真的好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.07,0:07:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.61,0:08:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然很好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.01,0:08:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.01,0:08:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,库洛是库洛，你是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.08,0:08:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟他比没有意义\N也不需要跟他比较
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.02,0:08:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了，别想那些了\N快睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.02,0:08:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.20,0:08:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的雪下得真大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.41,0:08:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就跟那天一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.78,0:08:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.54,0:08:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了，被你听到了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.45,0:08:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你一直提起库洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.58,0:08:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我不禁想起他死时的情景
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.85,0:08:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,库洛先生？\N对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.76,0:08:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是这个季节\N那天也下着这种大雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.86,0:08:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前他一直很健康的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.80,0:09:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是他突然说\N“我的寿命已尽，所以今天要分离了”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.14,0:09:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个人连临死前都好自私
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.54,0:09:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我总觉得他还活着\N到现在还在捉弄着我们呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.55,0:09:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了，为什么眼睛睁得那么大？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.48,0:09:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才说库洛先生\N或许还活着，说不定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.02,0:09:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我开玩笑的，开玩笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.16,0:09:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,库洛死时我跟月都在他身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.06,0:09:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不可能还活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.80,0:09:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是为什么\N每次发生怪事的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.73,0:09:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就会感觉到库洛先生的气息呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.90,0:09:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.04,0:09:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好库洛死前做了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.88,0:09:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去见他，确定这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.32,0:09:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去见谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.42,0:09:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,库洛先生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.05,0:09:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用“回”牌？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.86,0:09:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要回到过去的世界\N直接去问库洛先生的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.83,0:10:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说不定就可以了解最近的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.20,0:10:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是使用回牌\N会消耗很多的魔力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.67,0:10:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,万一中途发生什么事的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.04,0:10:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小可说只要借助\N月峰神社的樱树的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.21,0:10:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能够有办法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.87,0:10:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是还是太危险了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.65,0:10:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你为我担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.10,0:10:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.44,0:10:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“回”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.55,0:10:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.76,0:11:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要小心一点喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.64,0:11:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会回来，打钩钩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.91,0:11:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打钩钩，说谎的人会被千根针扎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.75,0:11:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一言为定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.75,0:11:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么待会儿见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.07,0:11:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.23,0:11:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请送我到\N库洛先生死去前的时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.24,0:11:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,库洛先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.23,0:12:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.80,0:12:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是小可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.31,0:12:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？可鲁贝洛斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.31,0:12:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来是月啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.48,0:12:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明已经春天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.62,0:12:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是只有这棵樱树还没有开花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.05,0:12:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很快就会开吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.19,0:12:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很快是什么时候？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.23,0:12:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是很快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.59,0:12:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.73,0:12:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这棵树真的会开花吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.37,0:12:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小可跟月在做什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.54,0:12:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们正在等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.62,0:13:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,库洛先生，我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.09,0:13:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.55,0:13:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.35,0:13:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，你太多事了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.80,0:14:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小可跟月好像很快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.98,0:14:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们两个好像都很幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.99,0:14:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你睡饱了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.60,0:14:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,库洛先生，我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.84,0:14:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里很凉，最适合睡午觉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.21,0:14:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的，我想请教您一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.71,0:14:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.05,0:14:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是从未来来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.72,0:14:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.15,0:14:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想问我的事是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.99,0:15:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为发生了一些…一些怪事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.20,0:15:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生在我身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.76,0:15:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后每次我都会感觉到您的气息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.53,0:15:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我在想\N会不会是你做了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.47,0:15:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我说我做了就有做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.01,0:15:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我说我没做我就没做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.94,0:15:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.88,0:15:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,库洛，我不是叫你\N不要用泡牌帮我洗吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.98,0:15:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.82,0:15:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.33,0:15:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们的感情真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.63,0:15:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好羡慕喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.67,0:15:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.54,0:15:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不喜欢这些孩子吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.94,0:15:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当然最喜欢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.58,0:15:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢小可、月\N还有库洛牌们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.88,0:15:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…可是我毕竟不是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.96,0:16:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下，库洛先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.90,0:16:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来夏天已经结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.71,0:16:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,季节似乎很自然地在交替着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.38,0:16:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有想过\N那种悲伤的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.42,0:16:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经想过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.59,0:16:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我就跟\N令人感觉到季节交替的落叶一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.67,0:16:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,库洛先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.19,0:17:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.76,0:17:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那张椅子是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.06,0:17:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我记得跟艾瑞尔家的椅子一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.50,0:17:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你快解释，库洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.47,0:17:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.87,0:17:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是我说的意思啊，月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.84,0:17:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我要离开这个世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.21,0:17:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个笑话不好笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.41,0:17:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾，这并不是笑话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.82,0:17:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.58,0:17:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的寿命已尽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.82,0:17:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寿命？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.82,0:17:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你的脾气古怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.49,0:17:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过库洛里德是\N全世界最厉害的魔法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.06,0:17:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被你创造出来的我们\N最清楚这点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.76,0:17:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此\N万物都一样有寿终的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.00,0:17:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也必须做准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.80,0:17:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.10,0:18:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备一个在我之后\N可以仁慈待你们的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.48,0:18:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要别的主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.81,0:18:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么就由你决定好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.02,0:18:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看那个人\N适不适合当你们的主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.25,0:18:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有人会适合的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.32,0:18:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有月一个人决定也不公平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.49,0:18:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,候补人选由可鲁贝洛斯来决定吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.23,0:18:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是说真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.23,0:18:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月、可鲁贝洛斯以及库洛牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.30,0:18:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是我倾全部心血及力量\N创造出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.44,0:18:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以，我希望在我死后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.51,0:18:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们也能在新主人身边\N幸福的过日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.38,0:18:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我最后的心愿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.99,0:18:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像季节不断交替一样\N人也是会不断地交替
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.36,0:18:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那才是活在这世上的人\N真正的姿态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.63,0:18:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那小可跟月怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.90,0:19:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才要你当他们的新主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.67,0:19:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得非常高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.98,0:19:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我恐怕…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.41,0:19:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，你一定没问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.82,0:19:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子就拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.82,0:19:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吗？小樱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.99,0:19:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.06,0:19:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我没有办法变成你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.47,0:19:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢小可跟月的那种感情\N不会输给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.54,0:19:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是就算那样\N我仍然不是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.08,0:19:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.92,0:19:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是你，绝对不会变成我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.99,0:19:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你只要在你的时间内\N努力的活下去就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.46,0:20:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的时间？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.30,0:20:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过去的事是无法改变或消失的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.10,0:20:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过，未来永远在你的面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.44,0:20:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看，冬天已经结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.53,0:20:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新的春天开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.33,0:20:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摊开看不见的地图寻找方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.84,0:20:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真正的光辉正在某处等着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.68,0:20:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,充满噪音的都市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.68,0:21:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快要无法呼吸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.02,0:21:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉中时间不断的流逝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.86,0:21:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要保持纯真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.07,0:21:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将灵感抛在脑后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.21,0:21:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迷失于迷宫时虽会感到迷惑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.65,0:21:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摊开看不见的地图…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.59,0:21:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.15,0:21:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是我，你是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.16,0:21:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你拥有只有你才能描绘的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.98,0:21:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧，小樱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.58,0:22:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有没有受伤？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.18,0:22:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.58,0:22:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？\N知道什么了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.22,0:22:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道你没见到库洛吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.49,0:22:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，我见到他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.39,0:22:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过我没有问他\N最近发生的究竟是什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.80,0:22:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你是去做什么的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.17,0:22:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过说也奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.60,0:22:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,库洛先生他们\N为什么会在艾瑞尔家呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.27,0:22:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾瑞尔？你是说你的同学吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.24,0:22:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么可能，库洛死的地方是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.18,0:22:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪，是在什么地方呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.02,0:22:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不记得了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.98,0:22:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关于那部分的记忆好像…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.49,0:22:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月也曾经到过艾瑞尔家\N可是他什么也没说耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.66,0:22:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记忆被消除了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.43,0:22:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是，是谁干的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.43,0:22:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是库洛里德的杰作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.44,0:23:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾瑞尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.71,0:23:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.65,0:23:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这一世的名字叫艾瑞尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.48,0:23:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而前世的名字叫库洛里德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:32.47,0:24:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办？大家都因为\N艾瑞尔的魔法而睡着了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.50,0:24:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果在天亮前无法破解魔法阵\N大家会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:41.07,0:24:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要试试看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:42.81,0:24:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定会有办法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:44.04,0:24:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对没问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:46.28,0:24:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,库洛魔法使\N“小樱与现身的库洛里德”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.48,0:24:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次也与小樱一起\N解除封印！
